sorry. That didn't work. I'll try again. It's a cool story about a
21-month fetus who was undergoing inutero surgery for spina bifida and
reached out of the incision to hold the Dr's hand. There's a beautiful
picture of it with the story. If I can't get it through to you on
e-mail, try to google for it. It's from a newspaper or magazine, I
think. Heidi
